Context: The academic divisions at George Brown College work with industry and community partners. Ways to engage include program or curriculum development, research projects collaboration, attending events, and connecting with graduates. Opportunities can be found by clicking on the academic divisions links on the left. For more information, sign up for updates, contact ask.george@georgebrown.ca, call 416-415-2000 or TTY 1-875-515-5559. The college's social media hub can also be visited. The information in the website is subject to change without notice and it should not be considered a representation, offer or warranty. Students are responsible for verifying George Brown College fee requirements.
